What are Nuclear Lifecycle Services?
Nuclear Lifecycle Services encompass specialized solutions that ensure the safe, efficient, and compliant management of nuclear facilities from conception through decommissioning. These services address three critical phases: design/construction (including regulatory compliance and safety engineering), operations/maintenance (plant optimization and safety management), and decommissioning/waste handling (safe dismantlement and radioactive material management).
